des:
Valley tech products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your VT-1W.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your VT-1W - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Valley tech products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our Valley tech app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our Valley tech app;
(3). You need to have some Valley tech devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our Valley tech app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in Valley tech skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search Valley tech skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of Valley tech, and you'll be navigated to Valley tech login page;
(9). Input your Valley tech account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the VT-1W.”
“Alexa,turn off the VT-1W.”
